Package xyz.model

Class Theme

java.lang.Object
org.json.JSONObject
xyz.model.ModelObject
xyz.model.Theme
public class Theme
extends ModelObject
Theme Models have associated HTML files which are currently default set to Index.html by the controller frameworks. Themes are also associated with a Palette string which should be a JSONArray passed by the client application.
